  "description": [
    "A r V Putnam Couuty Herald ISSUED EVERY THURSDAY Subserpiion Price 5 CeoU Year E L WIRT tOX Publishers Bntorad u 8eeond Clua Hail Matter at the Poat Office at Cuokeville Tana THURSDAY JANUARY 7 1914 1915 JANUARY 1915 M W T F S 10111213141516 9 I 171819202122 52627282950 PIEDMONT MO RFD No 1 DearEditor and Herald Readers If you will give me a little space in your good little paper I will write a few lines My papa takes H and I like it fine I like to go to school and am in the third grade Hike my teacher fine His name is Oscar Sheets I will close by asking for a shower of birthday cards as my birthday is the 21st day of December when I will be ten years old All cards will be ap preciated very much My address Is Evert Smith Piedmont Mo Dear Editor and Herald Readers If you will spare me a little space In one corner of your newsy little paper I wil chat a little whiie as my papa takes the good little paper and I like It fine I ike to go to school and am is the sixth"
